Indices.Message:
Slam your fist into the ground and surround
yourself
with pillars of alchemical metal. When performed
from high altitudes, the power of the attack
rises.
Can be activated even while in the air.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases amount of stakes
planted upon contact.
LV.6: Increases the times the pillars raise
(1→2).</COL>

Place your palm on the ground and upon raising it,
create waves of alchemical substances that spike
up along the ground.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases amount of stakes
planted upon contact.
LV.6: Increases number of waves (3→5) and adds the
ability to juggle enemies.</COL>

Create an elemental orb that bestows one of the
three main attributes of fire, ice, or lightning,
from the ground and place it in the air.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases duration of the
skill.
LV.6: Unlocks the final two elements, Holy and
Darkness.</COL>

Place an alchemical trampoline on the ground
that launches those who jump on it to high
altitudes.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases duration of the
skill.
LV.6: Allows placement in the air. When placed
mid-air, you can be launched horizontally.</COL>

Create a ball of wind-wrapped alchemical
substances.
Wind pressure is generated when striking the ball
after placement.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases duration of the
skill.
LV.6: Increases range of wind pressure generated
when struck.</COL>

Drive alchemical piles into enemies, and quickly
draw
their aggression. If a pile is struck, the amount
of
stakes on it will increase.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases duration of the
skill.
LV.6: Increases chase range of skill, and amount
of
alchemical stakes gained upon striking the
pile.</COL>

Generate a trap from an alchemical substance.
When enemies approach the trap, pillars spike out
from it and penetrate them.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases number of trap
activations.
LV.6: Increases the number of pillar spikes
(1→3).</COL>

Coat yourself in gold and deflect enemy attacks.
Enemies
that attack will build up the "Gilded" status
abnormality.
Can be activated even while in the air.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases rate of Gilding
build-up.
LV.6: Can activate the skill at anytime except
when grabbed.</COL>

Directly strike the enemy and detonate alchemical
stake on
target, creating a large explosion. Can be used
when climbing.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases damage of skill.
LV.6: Increases number of hits and the surrounding
enemies are affected by the explosion.</COL>

Jump up and form a trap from an alchemical
substance
in the air. When deployed, quickly launch
backwards.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases number of trap
activations.
LV.6: Allows activation while mid-air.</COL>

Shoot alchemical substances radially toward you.
If you are close to the enemies, all substances
will hit.
Can be activated in mid-air.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases damage.
LV.6: Increases range and the number of
substances (3→5).</COL>

Generate an area that nullifies damage for all
allies inside.
Enemies within the area are affected by your
chosen Elixir.
The duration is greatly increased with correct
timing.
<COL ffdc78>LV UP: Increases debilitation rate.
LV.6: Number of inputs increased, extending the
duration.</COL>

EX Additional Effects:
Increase damage.
The stake struck by this skill slowly builds up
automatically.
Can be used when climbing.

EX Additional Effects:
Increase status effect accumulation when
detonating the
stake struck by this skill using
Elixir/Alchemical Burst.

EX Additional Effects:
Increase damage.
Add Gilded status abnormality.
<COL ff7878>Further increase damage against
Human/Dragonkin/Alchemized enemies.</COL>

EX Additional Effects:
Increase physical and magick defense during
execution.
Increase endurance during execution.
Increase the amount of alchemical substance and
blow force.
Possible to use when being knocked back.

EX Additional Effects:
May employ strengthened alchemical substances
that deal
more damage and has faster alchemical buildup.
Normal alchemical substance has a chance to be
strengthened.
If used in conjunction with Counterra Aurum, all
substances
are strengthened.

EX Additional Effects:
Increase the number of alchemical waves created
and
generation speed.
Increase attack distance.
Inflict Physic/Magick Defense Down effects.

EX Additional Effects:
When you receive the enchant from this skill,
elemental
debilitation is greatly increased only on
yourself.

EX Additional Effects:
Grant enchantment to surrounding allies when you
place the
orb.
